N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 918.2 - Notification of compliance

State Regulations

Each of the said railroad corporations shall within 10
days from the date of service of this order notify the commissioner in writing
whether this order and all of its terms and requirements are accepted and will
be obeyed. Notes
